<hymn_number>1584</hymn_number>
<title>ʿạysẖyn lk bạlḥb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ʿạysẖyn lk bạlḥb wlyk kl ḥyạtnạ dy mlk ạ̹ydyk)2
 (ạ̹n ʿsẖnạ lyk wạ̹n mtnạ lyk)2 (mnk wlyk ʿạysẖyn lk ạ̹nt)2
 2- (ʿạysẖyn lk ʿạysẖyn lrḍạk wḥyạtnạ yḥyyhạ ndạk)2
 (trfʿ ạ̹ydynạ bqlwb ạ̉mynẗ)2 (wnqwl fạdynạ ʿạysẖyn lk ạ̹nt)2
 3- (ʿạysẖyn lk gẖrbẗ ạ̉yạm htʿdy wlw fyhạ ậlạm)2
 (ạ̹nt ạlṣdyq wạ̹nt ạlṭryq)2 (lw fyhạ ḍyq ʿạysẖyn lk ạ̹nt)2
 4- (ʿạysẖyn lk ʿạysẖyn llqạk mạsẖyyn lk mạsẖyyn wyạk)2
 (mạsk ạ̹ydnạ wạ̹nt ạlsfynẗ)2 (wạ̹nt ạlmdynẗ rạyḥyyn lk ạ̹nt)2</lyrics>
</song>